The main guidelines to use the application is :

1. Download the exe file on the pc/laptop you want to connect to
2. Download the apk file on the mobile phone you want to use and control the laptop.
3. While downloading the apk you may receive a pop up of unverified installation and such , therefore i assure you that you may 
proceed, but you can still run a scan on the pc using any antivirus software you may have. or directly check the files yourself.

4. THIS IS THE IMPORTANT THING , both the phone and the laptop/pc should be on the same wifi
5. Make sure any VPN is turned off.
6. Start the Exe while and also the application on your phone to connect you need to scan the qr code shown by the exe file 
7. Make sure that you don't share this qr code to anyone cause this may leak you ip address.
8. After a successfull connection the application will remember the last scanned System and auto connect to it (If the server side
is also up)
9. The app has a little latency issues and it would be needed to be fixed in later patches.
10. The application has been scanned by google for any threat but you may as well scan it to be cautious.

